title: Cajun blackened chicken
ingredients: ['1/2 teaspoon paprika', '1/4 teaspoon salt', '1/4 teaspoon cayenne pepper', '1/4 teaspoon ground cumin', '1/4 teaspoon dried thyme', '1/8 teaspoon ground white pepper', '1/8 teaspoon garlic powder', '2 skinless, boneless chicken breast fillets', '1 tablespoon vegetable oil']
